FBIS4-46258 "jptot023__l94044" JPRS-TOT-94-023-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 3 June 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA PALESTINIAN AFFAIRS Molotov Cocktails Hurled at Bethlehem Mayor's Home Molotov Cocktails Hurled at Bethlehem Mayor's Home TA0306082794 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 0400 GMT 3 Jun 94 TA0306082794 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el English BFN [Text] Three Molotov cocktails were hurled last night at the home of Bethlehem mayor Ilyas Frayj, who is also a member of the Palestinian Autonomy Authority. The door to his home was slightly damaged, but no one was hurt. This is the second time in two weeks Frayj's home has been the target of a Molotov cocktail attack.
